## Appendix B: Port Reference Quick Guide

```
EXTERNAL EXPOSURE (Public Internet):
443     HTTPS (Ingress)
80      HTTP (Redirect to 443)

KUBERNETES SERVICES (Cluster Internal):
5000    Main Application API
